{"tid":2145265,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國又有疫情爆發!中共又想改病毒名?","createTime":"2020-08-08T03:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T17:57:51.000Z","uid":222747,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3b7b5ff233d126cd9883120007fdc172032886f3","tid":2145265,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"近幾日新聞見到中國傳緊&ldquo;新布尼亞病毒&rdquo;,係乜嚟呢?<br />\nTOO LONG 唔識串就睇最尾紅字.<br />\n <br />\n睇番國際病毒分類委員會(ICTV)資料,隻病毒最早2014年係叫SFTS virus (發熱伴血小板減少綜合症, severe fever with thrombocytopenia syndrome)<br />\n2018改左做Huaiyangshan banyangvirus (WIKI:淮陽山病毒)<br />\n最新2019年果陣改左個病毒名為&ldquo;<span class=\"red\">Dabie bandavirus</span>&rdquo; (直譯:大別病毒)<br />\n<br />\n改名歷史SOURCE: ICTV Taxonomy history:  SFTS virus :<br />\n<a href=\"https://talk.ictvonline.org/taxonomy/p/taxonomy-history?taxnode_id=20141803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftalk.ictvonline.org%2Ftaxonomy%2Fp%2Ftaxonomy-history%3Ftaxnode_id%3D20141803&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDMrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=918f4814\" target=\"_blank\">https://talk.ictvonline.org/taxonomy/p/taxonomy-history?taxnode_id=20141803</a><br />\n<br />\n點解最終叫Dabie?因為Dabie係個起源地,英文WIKI咁講:<br />\nThe virus appears to have <span class=\"red\">originated in the Dabie Mountains</span>(大別山) in central China between 1918 and 1995.<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dabie_bandavirus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDabie_bandavirus&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDMrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=ce10b3b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dabie_bandavirus</a><br />\n改名文件都有講呢個原因:<br />\n... according to <span class=\"red\">the place of its first discovery</span>, ...<br />\n<a href=\"https://talk.ictvonline.org/ictv/proposals/2019.015M.zip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftalk.ictvonline.org%2Fictv%2Fproposals%2F2019.015M.zip&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDMrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=e9533ef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://talk.ictvonline.org/ictv/proposals/2019.015M.zip</a><br />\n<br />\n而WIKI D名亂到喊,中英文版本已經有出入<br />\n中文TITLE直接叫新布尼亞病毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E4%25BA%259A%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDMrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=2e6b3458\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92</a><br />\n睇番英文,係叫<span class=\"red\">Dabie bandavirus</span>囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dabie_bandavirus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDabie_bandavirus&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDMrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=ce10b3b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dabie_bandavirus</a><br />\n<br />\n但SEARCH 所有新聞竟然全部叫哂做&ldquo;<span class=\"red\">新布尼亞病毒</span>&rdquo;,甚至有D報紙竟然自創個英文叫&ldquo;<span class=\"red\">new bunyavirus</span>&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔該各界新聞媒體唔好再污名化&ldquo;布尼亞&rdquo;</span></span>,<br />\n中文請用番最廣為人知的&ldquo;<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">發熱伴血小板減少綜合症</span></span>&rdquo;,或者官方最新英文名的直譯:&ldquo;<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">大別病毒</span></span>&rdquo;<br />\n英文名更加應該用番最廣為人知的&ldquo;<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">SFTS virus</span></span>&rdquo;,或者官方最新英文名的&ldquo;<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">Dabie bandavirus</span></span>&rdquo;"},{"pid":"0587177ad9ebc62c0f360ec6edd3d2179c006db7","tid":2145265,"uid":105340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"世衛在佢手 龍門任佢擺"},{"pid":"722304df58879982f39aa7a9a8b6c4621c2594a4","tid":2145265,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b7b5ff233d126cd9883120007fdc172